Description_lang: Your abilities are amplified based on your current shapeshift form, granting an additional effect.$@spellicon197492 |CFFFFFFFFCaster Form|RRejuvenation heals for $s1% more and causes you to instantly generate $411231s1 Rage after entering Bear Form.$@spellicon197488 |CFFFFFFFFMoonkin Form|RWrath, Starfire, and Starsurge deal $s2% additional damage and cause you to instantly generate $411231s1 Rage after entering Bear Form.$@spellicon202155 |CFFFFFFFFCat Form|RRip, Ferocious Bite, and Maim deal $s3% additional damage and cause you to instantly generate ${$411231s1*2} Rage after entering Bear Form when cast with $s4 combo points.
